lead_paragraph: After Sunday's shooting in Florida, President Barack Obama has postponed a trip on Wednesday to Green Bay, Wisconsin, in which he would have participated in a campaign rally for Hillary Clinton, the White House said on Sunday.

headline.main: Obama Postpones Trip to Hillary Clinton Rally After Orlando Shooting
